以下是1.13版本的操作
org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack BukkitItem = new org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack(Material.apple);
net.minecraft.server.v1_13_R2.ItemStack NMSItem = org.bukkit.craftbukkit.v1_13_R2.inventory.CraftItemStack.asNMSCopy(BukkitItem);
net.minecraft.server.v1_13_R2.NBTTagCompound ItemNbt = = NMSItem.getTag();
然后就可以对ItemNbt操作了，比如:
ItemNbt.setString("key", "value");
以下操作是设置nbt
net.minecraft.server.v1_13_R2.NBTTagCompound nbt = new net.minecraft.server.v1_13_R2.NBTTagCompound();
nbt.setString("key", "value");
NMSItem.setTag(nbt);
